{"tid":2152833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍夾擊中国　B2A隱形轟炸機部署印度洋","createTime":"2020-08-12T08:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T05:40:50.000Z","uid":184679,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"250a82e4e87c35bf710efb4606e9c98a2a5342d6","tid":2152833,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200812/photo/bkn-20200812150240199-0812_00972_001_01p.jpg?20200812155441\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200812%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200812150240199-0812_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20200812155441&h=a6163d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nB2A是美軍隱形戰略轟炸機。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國繼續在印太地區部署兵力，加強對中國的軍事施壓。美軍3架B2A隱形戰略轟炸機周二（11日）飛越大半個地球，從本土經太平洋抵達印度洋戰略重地迪戈加西亞島。連同駐守西太平洋關島的B1B，意味美軍轟炸機東西兩翼「夾擊」中國。<br />\n<br />\n追蹤美國軍機動向的社交網帳戶Aircraft Spots周二發文，表示該批呼叫代號分別是REAPR11、REAPR12及REAPR13的B2A，從密蘇里州懷特曼空軍基地出發，取道太平洋夏威夷前往迪戈加西亞島，途中經過澳洲北部，沿途獲多架空中加油機支援。<br />\n<br />\n美軍對上一次在迪戈加西亞島部署這款轟炸機是2016年3月，當時美國太平洋空軍表明是回應南海局勢緊張，因此需要在印太地區提供持續及可靠的空中戰力。美軍暫未證實今次部署行動，但上月中已在關島安德森空軍基地部署2架B1B轟炸機。<br />\n<br />\n分析指，隨着美軍今年4月結束長達16年在關島的「持續轟炸機進駐」（CBP）任務，轟炸機特遣隊部署的性質出現改變，採用「動態武力運用」的作戰概念，部署規模及地點的形式不再固定，以符合國防戰略的戰略可預測性及作戰不可預測性。<br />\n<br />\n此外，迪戈加西亞島的地理位置，有利美軍從當地執行長程作戰飛行任務，覆蓋範圍包括太平洋、中東及東非。今次部署不但有針對中國的性質，亦包括維持對伊朗可能發起侵略的戒備，美軍今年1月初至3月底曾在該島部署6架B52H戰略轟炸機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200812/photo/bkn-20200812150240199-0812_00972_001_02p.jpg?20200812155441\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200812%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200812150240199-0812_00972_001_02p.jpg%3F20200812155441&h=fe0894a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAircraft Spots提供的B2A飛行路線圖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200812/photo/bkn-20200812150240199-0812_00972_001_04p.jpg?20200812155441\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20200812%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200812150240199-0812_00972_001_04p.jpg%3F20200812155441&h=4e35c6f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nB1B部署在關島安德森空軍基地<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20200812/bkn-20200812150240199-0812_00972_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"8182cb6f82bca53c5f0f6da6a162f0272f3e1318","tid":2152833,"uid":58209,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FLwH1rn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLwH1rn.jpg&h=6bae00c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWeVBZH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWeVBZH.jpg&h=73ca5da5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4d47d81edcfabe8953ab769bde8e0ed81f0edc3","tid":2152833,"uid":267810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8182cb6f82bca53c5f0f6da6a162f0272f3e1318","tid":2152833,"uid":58209,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FLwH1rn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLwH1rn.jpg&h=6bae00c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWeVBZH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWeVBZH.jpg&h=73ca5da5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca8d45ffc96e8b0c93195e5b4d7b0c8f06a8177a","tid":2152833,"uid":284284,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8182cb6f82bca53c5f0f6da6a162f0272f3e1318","tid":2152833,"uid":58209,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T08:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FLwH1rn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFLwH1rn.jpg&h=6bae00c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z